{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十三回巧逢故人。幽灵宫主以美色诱惑独孤伤，独孤伤中毒身亡。沈浪与幽灵宫主交手，掀开其面纱后震惊不已，幽灵宫主借粉红迷雾逃脱。可人与侍女们跳销魂舞后被快活王遣散。沈浪问及金无望，得知其已残废离去。快活王带沈浪进入内室，引见旧识白飞飞，并承诺展示真正的人间绝色。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来呀，来拿呀……你怕什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你摸摸看，我的心还在跳，我的胸膛也是暖和的……现在，这一切全都给你了，你为什么不来拿？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，随便什么人的心都对你没有用了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "牡丹花下死，做鬼也风流……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，他能瞧见我家宫主的胸膛，死了也算不冤枉了。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们也瞧见了这世上最美的胸膛，也可以死了。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，朝闻道，夕死而无憾矣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，已没有人干涉王爷了，王爷可以将心赐给贱妾了么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你连脸都不肯让本王瞧瞧，便想要本王的心，这岂非有些不公平？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷已瞧见了贱妾的身子，这还不够么……贱妾这样的身子．难道还不值王爷的区区一颗心么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你连身子都不惜被人瞧见，却不愿让人瞧见你的脸，这岂非怪事？莫非你的脸丑得不能见人？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若想瞧我的脸，自己来瞧吧。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是瞧过后莫要晕倒。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "衣香虽能杀死独孤伤，面纱中之迷香却未必杀得了沈浪……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既让我瞧，为何又要逃？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "手下留情些，莫要伤了她的香肌玉肤，花容月貌。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧王爷多么怜香惜玉，到此刻还一心体贴着你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "体贴的男人，女子最是欢喜，你为何不也学学王爷？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好男不和女斗，和女人打架的男人，可真没出息。",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓沈的，你听见了么……哎呀，王爷，你瞧他竟想摸我家宫主的胸口，你说他要不要脸。",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是本王，也想摸的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀，王爷，你……你难道不吃醋？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若想故意扰乱沈浪，那你就错了。纵有五百个人在他身旁打铁打鼓，他若想听不见，还是可以听不见的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼，装聋作哑，算什么本事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "装聋作哑，正是对付女人的最好本事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男人都不是好东西，只会一鼻孔出气，欺负女孩子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这颗心的滋味不知如何？我可得要尝一尝。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宫主小心。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你淫贼，你想将我怎样？放开我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不得了，来救人呀，沈浪抱住我家宫主要强奸她了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，我少不得要先亲亲你的脸。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你敢瞧我的脸，我就要你死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，沈浪，你就要她咬死你吧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪，你瞧过我的脸，你的眼珠子就是我的了，我迟早会来拿的……迟早会来拿的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎会是她……怎会是她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷，你……你也满足了么？",
      "tone": "喘息",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼丫头。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像我们这样的女孩子，一定可以令你满足的，你信不信？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你已证明了，本王怎能不信。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，王爷你就收留咱们吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "收留你们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我家宫主将我们抛在这里，显然已是不要我们了，她……她终究是个女人，但王爷你……舍得杀我们么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你想以自己的身子来换回活命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷你总是男人呀。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王怎会杀你们？若连你们这些小女子都不能放过，本王又怎能称天下之英雄，又怎能服得沈浪这样的豪士？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都去吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王……王爷不要我们……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们虽然自觉已诱惑得很，但在本王眼中瞧来，却只不过是一群还没有长成人形的小鬼而已，本王又怎会将你们瞧在眼里。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你方才一番做作，全是白费了心思。快些穿上衣服，乖乖的回家，下次若要再来时莫忘了把尿布也带来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "可人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这老鬼，你……你简直不是人！不是人……不是人……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_jing_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小精灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟在她们身后，追查出她们的落脚之处，即速回来禀报。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_jing_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小精灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王门下，果然没有一个等闲角色。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷之胸襟豪气，应变机智，当今天下，当真无人能及，而在下却力不能擒个小小的女子，实在愧对王爷。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那幽灵鬼女的容颜，竟能令沈浪也为之手软，想必定是天下之绝色，只可惜本王竟无缘一见。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她难道还不是王爷的掌中之物？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪呀沈浪，你不但知我，而且还救了我，却教本王如何待你？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下若不出手，那女子此刻只怕已是王爷的阶下囚，王爷还要如此说，岂不令沈浪愧煞。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非有你，那杯酒本王已喝下，此刻只怕已是她的阶下囚了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷难道真的不知酒中有毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王若知酒中有毒，为何要喝？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷已举杯，但却绝未沾唇。王爷那么做，只不过是要试试沈浪的眼力，是否能瞧破她的诡计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪深得我心……沈浪深得我心……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大战已过，本王理当犒劳于你，且让你见识本王的后宫佳丽。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下此刻最最想瞧见的，却是个极丑极丑的男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金无望？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷明鉴。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王只当你已忘怀了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "生平良友，岂能相忘。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能与金无望结为知己，当真不易；你敢在本王面前承认你与金无望友情深厚，更是难得。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷以诚相待，沈浪怎敢隐瞒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好……好，你此刻便要见他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下已等了许久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，本王这就叫他来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要瞧他，就打开箱子吧。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "属下手足已残，虽有再为王爷效死之心，却再无为王爷效忠之力。王爷以国士待属下，属下恨不能以死报知己，从此当流浪天涯，不知所去。然身负如山之恩，似海之仇，亦不敢从此自暴自弃，他日若有机缘，重得报恩复仇之力，当重归麾下，死不求去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恩怨分明，至死不忘，金无望可算是人间奇男子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但望他能如愿，恩仇两不相负。",
      "tone": "黯然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王属下四使，死的死，走的走，如今俱已散去，但本王此刻还如此开心发笑，你可知为了什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下不知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因本王有了你，以你一人之力，已可抵四使而有余。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只道男人瞧见美女时，要神魂颠倒，原来女人瞧见美男子时，也会这样子失魂落魄的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧她们怎样？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "俱都是美如天仙，艳如桃李。这就难怪王爷对方才那些小女子不屑一顾了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你钟意了谁，本王就送给你。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "古人有割爱赠妾的美事，千古来传为佳话，本王为何不能？何况，你再瞧这些丫头都如此瞧着你，若等她们效红拂之夜奔，本王倒不如索性大方些，无论你钟意了谁，只管说出就是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此中佳丽，本王敢夸纵是大内深宫中的妃子，也不过如此了，你难道连一个也瞧不上眼？",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却嫌脂粉污颜色。",
      "tone": "含笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪呀沈浪，你好高的眼色。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜王爷方才未曾瞧见那幽灵鬼女的面目。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只当那鬼女颜色真的已是天下无双？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笑而不语。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，本王不妨叫你见识见识真正的人间绝色。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "佳丽易得，绝色难求……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王此刻便带你去见一人，你见着她后，若还要说那幽灵鬼女乃是无双之绝色，本王就算输了。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你见着她后，千万莫要神魂颠倒。本王之一切，均可割爱相赠于你，只有她……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿她莫要教在下失望……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪呀沈浪，你本不该伤她们的心的！你此番不顾而去，可知那些女孩子是多么伤心、失望？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下本为鲁男子，怎及得王爷之怜香惜玉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个鲁男子……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘘——轻声些，脚步也放轻些，她身子柔弱，当不得惊吵。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是今天太早，而是昨夜太迟了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "莺儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，王爷每天早上都要来瞧瞧姑娘，只有今晚……哦，该说是昨夜，姑娘左等王爷也不来，右等王爷也不来，等得急死了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她真的会等得着急么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "莺儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还说不急，王爷若不信莺儿的话，问燕儿好了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_er",
      "speaker_name": "燕儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕儿也不知姑娘等得急不急，只瞧见姑娘在等时，将手中的一串茉莉球都揉碎了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "莺儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才喝了小半碗参汤，才算睡着。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "莺儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷此刻不如还是请到前面去喝两杯，等到姑娘醒来时，莺儿与燕儿再去请王爷过来好么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只是轻轻走进去瞧瞧她好么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "莺儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷要进去，谁敢阻拦。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_er",
      "speaker_name": "燕儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是王爷明知姑娘最易惊醒，姑娘睡着时，谁也不准打扰，这话也是王爷自己说出来的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么……那么……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是王爷来了么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你睡吧，你睡吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "莺儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明明将别人吵醒了，还叫别人睡吧。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王少时再来就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷既然来了，为何不进来。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进去岂非惊吵了你？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷来了，贱妾纵然几天睡不着，也是欢喜的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，本王就进来了……只是，这里还有位客人，也想见见你，不知你可愿意见他么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷既将他带到这里来，他想必定是超群出众的人物，贱妾有幸得见如此人物，也高兴得很。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你听，她那张小嘴多讨人欢喜。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然不凡。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贱妾无力站起迎驾，王爷恕罪。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你躺着……你只管躺着……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位沈浪沈公子，一心想瞧瞧你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷明知贱妾是认得沈公子的，为何还要故意这么说？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦，原来你说的那位沈公子，就是这位沈公子呀。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贱妾昔日流浪江湖时，若非这位沈公子多次搭救，现在……现在只怕就不能侍候王爷了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，本王倒真该谢谢他才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈公子今日居然也会来到这里，贱妾当真是不胜欣喜。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好教你得知，他此刻已与本王是一家人了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这是真的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王纵骗尽世上所有人，也不会骗你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这真是天大的喜事，贱妾无论如何，也得置酒敬两位一杯。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫要劳动，本王要喝酒，自会找别人伺候。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷放心，贱妾此刻已好得多了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况，今天是两位绝代英雄见面的日子，贱妾若不能亲手为两位置酒，实在是终身遗憾。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她什么都好，就是身子太单薄了些。",
      "tone": "叹气",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "名花已得名主，沈浪徒唤奈何。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪呀沈浪，你莫非在吃本王的醋么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷岂不正是希望沈浪吃醋么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪之能，万夫莫敌；沈浪之唇，亦是万夫莫敌。上天若只准本王在白飞飞与沈浪两人中选择其一，本王宁择沈浪。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷如此说，当真胜过千万句夸奖沈浪的言语。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我如此待你，但愿你日后莫要负我。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "知遇之情，永生不忘。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，绝代之英雄与美人尽属于我，本王今日岂能不醉。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 766
    }
